<h3>Import events for a new geography</h3>

<p>
  To add or update events for geography you first have to know the ID of geography and use Events importer.
</p>

<p>
  When adding new geographies with events the good practice would be to first create geographies in draft state.
  After the upload, you can download newly created geographies filtering by draft state and created date.
  You will have Ids that you can use in Events CSV file. Eventable type must be set to "Geography", Eventable Id - those
  would be downloaded ids, and you can add an extra column "Eventable Title" with geography name to know for which
  geography you are creating a new event. Any extra column not mentioned in columns descriptions will be ignored.
</p>

